name: dfs.short.circuit.shared.memory.watcher.interrupt.check.ms
description:
The length of time in milliseconds that the short-circuit shared memory
    watcher will go between checking for java interruptions sent from other
    threads.  This is provided mainly for unit tests.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-user-done-dir.permissions
description:
The permissions of the user directories in
  ${mapreduce.jobhistory.intermediate-done-dir}. The user and the group
  permission must be 7, this is enforced.

name: file.bytes-per-checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  file.stream-buffer-size

name: dfs.client.write.max-packets-in-flight
description: The maximum number of DFSPackets allowed in flight.

name: dfs.ha.zkfc.port
description:
The port number that the zookeeper failover controller RPC
    server binds to.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.container.log.limit.kb
description:
The maximum size of the MRAppMaster attempt container logs in KB.
    0 disables the cap.

name: dfs.namenode.list.cache.directives.num.responses
description:
This value controls the number of cache directives that the NameNode will
    send over the wire in response to a listDirectives RPC.

name: mapreduce.job.encrypted-intermediate-data.buffer.kb
description:
Buffer size for intermediate encrypt data in kb
  default is 128
